item.title: CVE-2020-2108|2024-08-04T07:01:39.769Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20websphere%20deployer%20plugin
item.description: Jenkins WebSphere Deployer Plugin 1.6.1 and earlier does not configure the XML parser to prevent XXE attacks which can be exploited by a user with Job/Configure permissions.
